{"type":"article_comment","id":338893,"parentType":"article","parentId":17511,"uid":3685,"contents":"<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/item_id-338890#\"><blockquote>习对密宗的着迷由来以久，这个说法不是空穴来风 </blockquote></a><br>\n如果真让🐻搞成了史上第一次有西藏喇嘛深度参与的文化大革命，那毛泽东岂不是要气的从纪念堂水晶棺里蹦出来啪啪抽🐻嘴巴子<br>\n所以我说爆料过于离奇，还不如说火箭里放的是习主席像章（文革期间东方红二号三号确实搭载了毛像章）<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C7-Cf4tV4AALcJd?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C7-Cf4tV4AALcJd?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C7-Cf4tV4AALcJd?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-04-10","agreeCount":7,"discussionCount":0}